	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />But why does the ROM info on the emulator show 32kb PRG and 8kb CHR mapper 64, mirror V for the released version? My shows mapper 0, mirror H. What does Vertical/Horizontal Mirroring mean?

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
