	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Because your ROM is a hack, not the release version.  The real ROM uses mapper 0 and horizontal mirroring (not that it matters much when the game doesn't scroll the screen.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


